            "reviews": "“Some truly gorgeous moments in the game will leave you speechless. The sound design is great too, making some environments that shouldn’t be scary terrifying.”<br>71/100 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://cogconnected.com/review/inner-friend-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >COGconnected</a><br><br>“While each memory deals with a different fear and theme, the game’s unnerving tone and atmosphere persist throughout.”<br>7/10 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://culturedvultures.com/the-inner-friend-pc-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Cultured Vultures</a><br><br>“The creative team left no stone un-turned in building their world, providing as much for the ears as for the eyes.”<br>4.5/5 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.ihorror.com/playminds-the-inner-friend-is-a-fantastic-internalized-game-of-horrors/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >iHorror</a><br>",
